  "text": "The crude extracts were then freeze dried (Heto Drywinner\u00ae DW-3), put into 0.5 L amber glass jars and kept in a refrigerator at -4 \u00b0C. A sample of these extracts was used to test for flavonoids according to [CITATION_1] .",
